  "body": "At present, blobs are retained for a default period of 4096 epochs, approximately 18 days, as defined by `MIN_EPOCHS_FOR_BLOB_SIDECARS_REQUESTS` in the specification. It would be beneficial to introduce a (potentially hidden) flag that permits users to extend this retention duration.\r\n\r\n**Proposed Solution:**\r\n1. Introduce a new flag, e.g., `--extend-blob-retention`.\r\n2. When this flag is set, allow users to specify the desired retention period.\r\n3. Ensure backward compatibility so that the default 4096 epochs retention remains unchanged if the flag is not used.\r\n4. If the node restarts with a different `blob-retention` value, it should fail to start until the node wipes the DB",
